metadata.name: X Rabbit #1
metadata.description:
X Rabbits Club (XRC) consists of 7,502 NFTs, which are featured with uniqueness and high liquidity guaranteed by Ethereum network, and will never be lost owing to their storage in IPFS.

XRC was derived from an IP in China called Lengtoo, which was established in 2010 and has more than 65 million followers across the web. As the first NFT project, XRC is on a mission to enter the new world of Web3 and strive for its development, as well as provide the soil for millions of creators to grow.
